# f5distributedcloud_known_label (Data Source)

The `f5distributedcloud_known_label` data source retrieves information about an existing known label.

## Example Usage

```hcl
data "f5distributedcloud_known_label" "example" {
  name      = "my-known-label"
  namespace = "shared"
}

output "label_key" {
  value = data.f5distributedcloud_known_label.example.label_key
}
```



<!-- schema generated by tfplugindocs -->
## Schema

### Required

- `name` (String) Name of the known label to look up.
- `namespace` (String) Namespace where the known label is located.

### Read-Only

- `description` (String) Description of the known label.
- `id` (String) Unique identifier of the known label.
- `label_key` (String) Key of the known label.
